<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c2">(خ حم)</span> ,<span class="c5"> وَعَنْ سَعِيدِ بْنِ جُبَيْرٍ قَالَ:</span> قَالَ لِي ابْنُ عَبَّاسٍ: هَلْ تَزَوَّجْتَ؟ ,<span class="c5"> قُلْتُ:</span> لَا ,<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> فَتَزَوَّجْ , <span class="c1">" فَإِنَّ خَيْرَ هَذِهِ الْأُمَّةِ <span class="c2">(١)</span> <span class="c4">[كَانَ]</span> <span class="c2">(٢)</span> أَكْثَرَهَا نِسَاءً "</span> <span class="c2">(٣)</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
